{
  "texts": [
    "The graph was made according to the occurrence of each principle.",
    "An example of a correct graph interpretation is that 92 tools can facilitate compliance with the Explicability principle in the Performance Evaluation stage",
    "Our research identified 352 tools (from now on referred to interchangeably as resources) that have made it possible to complete the typology described in the previous section.",
    "Each resource was examined and categorized based on the life cycle stage, high-level principle, resource type, task type, and level of development.",
    "Other data were also collected, such as the sector that created the tool, year of creation, links of interest, and programming language (applicable to technical tools)."
  ]
}